    <p>{`On this page, we explain step by step how to setup `}<strong parentName="p"><a parentName="strong" {...{
          "href": "https://magento.com/"
        }}>{`Magento 2`}</a></strong>{` with `}<strong parentName="p">{`CloudPanel`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "installation"
    }}>{`Installation`}</h2>
    <p>{`In the following example we will setup a `}<strong parentName="p"><a parentName="strong" {...{
          "href": "https://magento.com/"
        }}>{`Magento`}</a></strong>{` shop under the domain `}<strong parentName="p"><em parentName="strong"><a parentName="em" {...{
            "href": "http://www.domain.com"
          }}>{`www.domain.com`}</a></em></strong>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "elasticsearch"
    }}>{`Elasticsearch`}</h2>
    <p>{`The latest `}<strong parentName="p">{`Magento 2`}</strong>{` version requires `}<strong parentName="p">{`Elasticsearch 7.9`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`A step by step guide how to install `}<strong parentName="p">{`Elasticsearch 7.9`}</strong>{` on `}<strong parentName="p">{`Debian 10`}</strong>{` can be found on the following site: `}</p>
    <p><a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/7.9/deb.html"
      }}>{`https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/7.9/deb.html`}</a></p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "preparation"
    }}>{`Preparation`}</h3>
    <p>{`Before we can start with the installation, we need to create an `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "../frontend-area/users#adding-a-user"
      }}>{`SSH User`}</a>{`, a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "../frontend-area/databases#adding-a-database"
      }}>{`Database`}</a>{`, and a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "../frontend-area/domains#adding-a-domain"
      }}>{`Domain`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`When you `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "../frontend-area/domains#adding-a-domain"
      }}>{`Add the Domain`}</a>{`, make sure to select the `}<strong parentName="p">{`Magento 2 Vhost Template`}</strong>{` and the right `}<strong parentName="p">{`PHP Version`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
    <img class="border" src={useBaseUrl('img/v1/applications/magento-2/new_domain.png?v=1')} /> <br /><br />
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-warning alert alert--danger"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
